<div id="pf4426" class="pf w4f h303" data-page-no="4426"><div class="pc pc4426 w4f h303"><div class="t m1bd1 x74 h49 y15a7 ff3 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Your Adventist Neighbors </div><div class="t m271 x74 h69 y580 ff2 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">by Richard Utt. </div><div class="t m46d x74 h69 y53c ff2 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Who are Seventh-day Adventists? You </div><div class="t m296 x61 h69 y414 ff2 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">can&apos;t give the answer in just a few </div><div class="t m868 x61 h69 y7ac ff2 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">words or in just a few minutes. This little </div><div class="t m649 x61 h69 ya5b ff2 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">book tells what Adventists believe </div><div class="t m9f9 x61 h69 yc3b ff2 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">and why, along with an invitation to </div><div class="t m563 x61 h69 y8b3 ff2 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">join us. $.75 </div><div class="t m1500 x61 h49 ya2d ff3 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Through the Bible in 55 Minutes </div><div class="t m329 x61 h69 y1876 ff2 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">by H. M. S. Richards, Jr. </div><div class="t m44c x61 h69 y8b8 ff2 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">For the unbeliever this little book will </div><div class="t m3e5 x61 h69 y666 ff2 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">whet his appetite and hopefully will </div><div class="t m37e x61 h69 y893 ff2 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">lead him to the full truths and accept-</div><div class="t mdf4 x61 h69 yec9 ff2 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">ance of Heaven&apos;s most gracious pro-</div><div class="t m61c x61 h69 y1916 ff2 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">visions for eternal life. It gives the </div><div class="t m1be x61 h69 y824 ff2 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">reader an overall view of the 66 </div><div class="t md00 x61 h69 y76d ff2 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">books of the Bible in one sitting. $.75 </div><div class="t mfb6 x61 h49 yaae ff3 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">The Mightiest Lover of All </div><div class="t m83e x61 h69 y726 ff2 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">by Lawrence Maxwell. </div><div class="t mec4 x61 h69 y5a0 ff2 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">This is one of the favorite Bible stories </div><div class="t m646 x61 h69 y19cf ff2 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">of young and old alikeâ€”that of Sam-</div><div class="t m296 x61 h69 y657 ff2 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">son, one whom God loved though </div><div class="t m5c8 x64 h69 y1043 ff2 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">unlovely. If God loved Samson, with </div><div class="t m1105 x64 h69 y1257 ff2 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">all his faults and failures, there is cer-</div><div class="t m26e x61 h69 y250 ff2 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">tainly hope for you and me. This story </div><div class="t m7e3 x64 h69 y1642 ff2 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">was written to tell us about God and </div><div class="t m766 x64 h69 y2eb ff2 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">His great love for each one of us. $.50 </div><div class="t m1ae4 x64 h49 y137e ff3 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Pass It On: In Praise of Sharing Talents </div><div class="t m3da x64 h69 y90f ff2 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">by Carol Amen. </div><div class="t ma30 x7 h69 y15a7 ff2 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">A unique little book which describes </div><div class="t m477 x7 h69 y1289 ff2 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">real experiences showing the value </div><div class="t m1578 x7 h69 ya43 ff2 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">and rewards of helping other people. </div><div class="t m105c x7 h69 y7ee ff2 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">The author clearly shows how you </div><div class="t m85c x7 h69 y7ad ff2 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">can help people In many ways by </div><div class="t m8d8 x7 h69 ya45 ff2 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">sharing your talents. $.50 </div><div class="t md05 x7 h49 yc3a ff3 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Hurting </div><div class="t m43b x7 h69 y77c ff2 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">by Dan Day. </div><div class="t mfc x7 h69 ya2d ff2 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">The book deals with the common </div><div class="t m698 x7 h69 y8e ff2 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">problem of how to overcome emo-</div><div class="t m692 x7 h69 y126b ff2 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">tional hurt. The author discusses sev-</div><div class="t m117c x7 h69 y496 ff2 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">eral &quot;things to do&quot;:1. Leave the person </div><div class="t m116a x7 h69 y893 ff2 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">who hurt you in God&apos;s hands. 2. Don&apos;t </div><div class="t m13ad x7 h69 y4e6 ff2 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">become self-righteous. 3. Recognize </div><div class="t m356 x7 h69 y217 ff2 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">that good people sometimes do bad </div><div class="t mb06 x7 h69 y80a ff2 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">things. </div><div class="t m24a x91 h49 y4af ff3 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">4. </div><div class="t m6f4 xa0 h69 y471 ff2 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Forgive. 5. Discover the </div><div class="t m303 x7 h69 y3a6 ff2 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">place of healing at the foot of the </div><div class="t mfe x7 h69 y13ea ff2 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">cross. $.50 </div><div class="t m8a6 x7 h69 y66 ff2 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">These books are available at your </div><div class="t m132f x7 h69 ya79 ff2 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">local Adventist Book Center. </div><div class="t m14b6 x7 h69 y475 ff2 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Prices in U.S. currency. </div><div class="t m93 xae h69 y910 ff2 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Brought to you by Pacific Press </div></div><div class="pi" data-data='{"ctm":[1.000000,0.000000,0.000000,1.000000,0.000000,0.000000]}'></div></div>
